        "text": "=📚 *KB Auto-Updater* | `{{ $json.action.toUpperCase() }}`\n\n*{{ $json.article_title }}*\n*Category:* {{ $json.category }} | *Difficulty:* {{ $json.difficulty_level }} | *Read Time:* {{ $json.estimated_read_time }}\n*Confidence:* {{ $json.confidence }}/10\n\n*Summary:* {{ $json.article_summary }}\n\n*Source:* `{{ $json.ticket_id }}` — {{ $json.ticket_title }}\n\n{{ $json.action === 'skip' ? '⏭️ Skipped: ' + ($json.skip_reason || 'Too specific to generalize') : ($json.action === 'create' ? '✅ New article drafted in Notion — review and publish when ready.' : '🔄 Existing article updated in Notion.') }}",
